Revision history for Perl extension Class::Monadic

0.04 Sat Mar 28 12:49:40 2009
	- add add_methods() as an alias of add_method()
	- add add_fields()  as an alias of add_field()
	- fix t/09_leaktrace.t
	- add Test::LeakTrace to test_requires

0.03 Thu Mar  5 10:20:44 2009
	- add $meta->bless() method to copy its features into an object
	- enable $obj->clone()
	- enable Class::Monadic->initialize(\*FILEHANDLE)

0.02 Sun Feb 22 14:44:03 2009
	- fix memory leaks
	- extend $meta->add_field() to accept validators
	- deny $obj->clone() and Storable::freeze($obj) explicitly

0.01 Thu Feb  5 22:16:52 2009
	- original version; created by Module::Setup
